{
  "info": {
    "name": "04 - Rooms API",
    "description": "Collection complète pour tester l'API Rooms du système ComHotel.\n\n**Fonctionnalités testées:**\n- CRUD complet des chambres\n- Validation des données (RoomType, ViewType, capacités)\n- Filtres (par hôtel, par statut actif/inactif)\n- Soft delete\n- RBAC (Admin, Owner, Guest)\n\n**Variables requises:**\n- `base_url`: URL de l'API (ex: http://localhost:3000)\n- `admin_token`: Token JWT pour admin\n- `owner_token`: Token JWT pour hotel owner\n- `guest_token`: Token JWT pour guest\n- `hotel_id`: ID d'un hôtel existant\n\n🤖 Généré automatiquement par le système agentique ComHotel",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "room_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "hotel_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "admin_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "owner_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "guest_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup - Get Tokens",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login as Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200 or 201\", function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has accessToken\", function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@comhotel.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login as Hotel Owner",
          "event": [
            {
